text: Seal Sanctuary in Hel The Seal Sanctuary in Hel (Fokarium w Helu) is a public aquarium in the town of Hel at the Polish seaside of the Baltic Sea. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Aquaria in Poland Category:Tourist attractions in Pomeranian Voivodeship Category:Buildings and structures in Pomeranian Voivodeship
